snippet: Gunmen drove into Tahrir Square in Cairo on Monday and fired at an antigovernment sit-in, seriously wounding a protester.
abstract: Gunmen drive in Tahrir Square in Cairo, firing on antigovernment sit-in and seriously wounding activist Muhanad Samir, who witnesses believe was targeted.
lead_paragraph: Gunmen drove into Tahrir Square in Cairo on Monday and fired at an antigovernment sit-in, seriously wounding a protester.

headline.seo: Protester Wounded by Gunmen in Egypt
